Class CreationConstraints

  • java.lang.Object
    • es.us.isa.aml.translator.builders.wsag.model.CreationConstraints

  • public class CreationConstraints
extends java.lang.Object
    This optional element of an Agreement expresses the constraints for creating/negotiating an agreement. It contains any number of offer items and constraints in any order.
